{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A cute and approachable turn-based deck builder/card battler that combines the battle systems from Tetra Master/Triple Triad and Pok\u00e9mon. Collect, upgrade, and customize your party to strategically defeat your opponents and save them from the attack on Hex Island.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305380/extras/text-capture.png?t=1729187469\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305380/extras/gif-capture.gif?t=1729187469\" />Use your arrows to capture the opponent's tokens and convert them into your color. The player with the most tokens in their color at the end of the match wins.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">When arrows connect, a battle is triggered and dice are rolled. Battles may add risk, but allow for additional captures through combos. Element types are vital to your success, and will provide an attack boost when used against weaker elements.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305380/extras/text-choose.png?t=1729187469\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305380/extras/gif-abilities.gif?t=1729187469\" />Discover different ways to outwit your opponent and secure the win. Some tokens contain Special Abilities, each with its own unique effect.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305380/extras/gif-board.gif?t=1729187469\" />Keep an eye out for Walls, Field Elements, Bombs, and other obstacles found on the board that can also be used to your advantage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305380/extras/text-collect.png?t=1729187469\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305380/extras/gif-loot.gif?t=1729187469\" />Grow your collection of tokens and critters by looting your opponent after a victory, opening booster packs, and finding treasure chests.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305380/extras/text-customize.png?t=1729187469\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305380/extras/booster.png?t=1729187469\" />Tokens come in a variety of designs, elements, abilities, and arrow compositions, allowing you to create a unique party that best fits your playstyle. You can also upgrade and modify your tokens in order to have the upper hand during your next match.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305380/extras/text-challenge.png?t=1729187469\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305380/extras/pvp-lobby.png?t=1729187469\" />Engage in friendly exhibition matches against other players, or put your friendship to the test by looting all of their tokens! Customize the board to your advantage, or leave it to chance and adapt your strategy as you play.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305380/extras/text-connect.png?t=1729187469\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305380/extras/token-socials.png?t=1729187469\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Join our Discord to leave feedback and get updates, and subscribe to our YouTube channel to see what games we're working on next!</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Practice Makes Perfect","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2305380/4489b181174627761e68478523a3d2ab475df889.jpg"},{"name":"Chicken Dinner","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2305380/d55521a4bcbfc137cc0e465fed6a2b9441ef6ec5.jpg"},{"name":"Pentakill","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2305380/4d65722766f95d142fb7ce65b6a846d5b8a74d7f.jpg"},{"name":"My Precious","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2305380/e71b8a3ffc86dd8276775db2c33cc1c5558410bb.jpg"},{"name":"Attack on Hex Island!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2305380/f49cdd02b6eb975c6b83278df3acec3ab8762ed6.jpg"},{"name":"Unbeatable","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2305380/54c2336063932171ae74d86477f2ef7fbdb8b17a.jpg"},{"name":"Fully Loaded","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2305380/b930f03f2598b23bc5feeb841c1243b51a958731.jpg"},{"name":"The Prodigal Son","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2305380/7000fe3ddd8d9cff8bddb513ab511d939c28b903.jpg"},{"name":"Root of All Evil","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2305380/d36df4c408785847323fff18e1809a3c94a10f87.jpg"},{"name":"Gotta Catch 'Em All","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2305380/ec014f2cd531b3d429b64e6bde21e50366674a89.jpg"}],"total":50},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305380/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1729187469","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305380/page.bg.jpg?t=1729187